{
  "stem": "1704.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 244.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had a nurse on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said, I've got people who had been sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I want them to go on the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the others had to walk for a mile to the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got on the truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had a little boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, you take him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You take him, So I don't have to carry him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Little did we know, had that happened in one of the other camps, that whole truck would have gone straight to the gas chambers, that little boy as well.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there were no gas chambers in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it ended up all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went straightaway in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They made a hospital available for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was there a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Could you tell me about the hospital?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it wasn't much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't ready.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a barrack with a few beds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But lucky, you know, I wasn't very sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was only recuperating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Westerbork was better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in Belsen they had--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they called it a revere, the hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a doctor, a very good doctor, Greek.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Greek were there already, Greek Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the head of the camp was Greek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All barracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All barracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was out in the middle of a forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you could see trees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was very, very big.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when you went out of the gate, you know, when people who worked outside the camp had to go out of the gate, and they would walk for miles.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there was another camp, but I don't know what was behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
